Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:02.60,EN,,0,0,0,,This plant wall I put up on my balcony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.95,EN,,0,0,0,,earlier this year — honestly, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.10,EN,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't mounted very securely,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.90,EN,,0,0,0,,so by now, about half of it has fallen down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.30,EN,,0,0,0,,To make it sturdier,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.10,EN,,0,0,0,,this time I'm setting it up a whole different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.40,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm using a rolling rack as the frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.60,EN,,0,0,0,,and locking each pot in place with nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.20,EN,,0,0,0,,so everything stays nice and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.30,EN,,0,0,0,,It can even spin a full three-sixty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:25.10,EN,,0,0,0,,and roll around freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.95,EN,,0,0,0,,And the size fits the balcony just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.40,EN,,0,0,0,,You just drop the inner pot with the plant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.45,EN,,0,0,0,,into the outer planter, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.70,EN,,0,0,0,,Right now it's looking a little too green —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:36.55,EN,,0,0,0,,it could use more variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.80,EN,,0,0,0,,So next, I'll pick up some brighter, more colorful plants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:42.50,EN,,0,0,0,,to liven the whole thing up.
